    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world, transformed by a cataclysmic event, is seeing new forms of life emerge in the midst of humans. And among them, divines have appeared to guide the survivors to the only continent left on earth. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You take on the role of one of these divines, with the aim of leading your people to the continent, while trying to convince, or eliminate, the people who stand in your way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Expand your village <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286460/extras/72ef15add33a8515aab4854fca7ac35f.poster.avif?t=1743008746\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286460/extras/72ef15add33a8515aab4854fca7ac35f.webm?t=1743008746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286460/extras/72ef15add33a8515aab4854fca7ac35f.mp4?t=1743008746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your village, build houses and many other buildings to keep your villagers happy and prosperous. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assign them roles and professions within the village to ensure it runs smoothly. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your influence to extend your reach and impress neighbouring villages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use your divine powers for good ... or evil  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286460/extras/7eb4b781d30d6ab924b9c49ce5b908fe.poster.avif?t=1743008746\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286460/extras/7eb4b781d30d6ab924b9c49ce5b908fe.webm?t=1743008746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286460/extras/7eb4b781d30d6ab924b9c49ce5b908fe.mp4?t=1743008746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Use over 20 spells to protect, destroy or manipulate your villagers or those of your divine opponents.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be careful, all your actions will have an impact on your town, its visual style, the style of your villagers and their behaviour, and may open up new ways of playing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Follow the lives of your villagers<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286460/extras/341cfcd450a5aa7e443a577d742dd312.poster.avif?t=1743008746\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286460/extras/341cfcd450a5aa7e443a577d742dd312.webm?t=1743008746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286460/extras/341cfcd450a5aa7e443a577d742dd312.mp4?t=1743008746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your villagers have a life of couples, families and work, and take time out to relax. Meet their needs to keep them as happy as possible (in their own way) and earn rewards for expanding and decorating your village.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customise your villagers with over 1,200 combinations of clothes, hairstyles, tattoos and more...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play with and against your friends</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286460/extras/87bab5a28017b5018ae48116b70f15a6.poster.avif?t=1743008746\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286460/extras/87bab5a28017b5018ae48116b70f15a6.webm?t=1743008746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286460/extras/87bab5a28017b5018ae48116b70f15a6.mp4?t=1743008746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to the single-player campaign mode &amp; classic single-player games, you can play in co-op with your friends, or against them to establish yourself as the ultimate divine being.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
